<!-- @context: typescript, pnpm, vitest, eslint, prettier -->

## TypeScript Development (pnpm template)

**Package manager**: Always use `pnpm` -- never `npm` or `yarn`.

**Common commands:**
- `mise run install` -- install all deps (`pnpm install`)
- `mise run build` -- compile TypeScript (`tsc` -> `dist/`)
- `mise run test` -- run vitest test suite
- `mise run lint` -- ESLint + `tsc --noEmit` (type errors surface here)
- `mise run lint-fix` -- ESLint auto-fix (does not fix type errors)
- `mise run format` / `mise run format-check` -- Prettier format / check
- `mise run publish` -- publish to npm (requires `NPM_TOKEN`)

**Adding dependencies:**
- Runtime: `pnpm add <package>`
- Dev/test only: `pnpm add -D <package>`

**Source layout:**
- `src/index.ts` -- public API (re-exports from lib modules)
- `src/lib.ts` -- library implementation
- `tests/` -- vitest tests
- `dist/` -- compiled output (gitignored, published to npm)

**Import paths**: Standard imports -- no `.js` extension required:
```typescript
import { greet } from './lib';
```

**Testing (vitest):**
- Tests in `tests/` directory; run with `mise run test`
- Watch mode: `pnpm run test -- --watch`
- Coverage: `pnpm run test -- --coverage`

**Publishing to npm:** (requires an npm Automation token set as `NPM_TOKEN` in CI secrets)
- `mise run publish` -- calls `pnpm publish --access public --no-git-checks`
- Set `NODE_AUTH_TOKEN` env var: `export NODE_AUTH_TOKEN=npm_xxx...`
- In CI: add `NPM_TOKEN` to GitHub repository secrets (Settings -> Secrets and variables -> Actions); the workflow maps it to `NODE_AUTH_TOKEN` automatically
- Scoped packages: update `"name"` in `package.json` to `"@your-org/package"`
- Pre-release: `mise run publish-rc` -- publishes to npm with `--tag next`
- **Token expiry**: npm Granular tokens expire after 90 days -- rotate before expiry or configure Trusted Publishing (OIDC) to avoid tokens entirely (see `docs/user-guide.md`)

**Code style (ESLint + Prettier):**
- ESLint flat config in `eslint.config.js` with `@typescript-eslint`
- Prettier config in `.prettierrc`: 120 char line length, single quotes
- Run `mise run lint-fix && mise run format` to auto-fix everything
